headline: Consumers Energy Alerts Customers to Be on Guard Against New Scam that Demands Immediate Payment
summary: Consumers Energy is alerting Michiganders to be on the lookout of scammers who this week have been contacting people and demanding immediate payment with a bogus threat that their service will be shut off.
